<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Michelle, I&apos;m not sure what &apos;good for 25 M.E.&apos; means. If you are speaking of ME/CFS, that is what I have. I found this book incredibly helpful, even t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Michelle, I'm not sure what 'good for 25 M.E.' means. If you are speaking of ME/CFS, that is what I have. I found this book incredibly helpful, even though it offers no suggestions for medical treatment. It is not a cure for anything, just a way to live better with what you have. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
