        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4096535929" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9204444228537183097">Honestly, more like two stars -- not in my opinion a very accurate representation of core Buddhist teachings, the amount of focus on the autobiographical seemed very heavy. More than anything, it felt quite redundant &amp; &quot;padded&quot; -- would have made a decent blog post of a couple pages, but really for me not even enough meaningful content to merit a full article, let alone a book. But that said, I definitely feel for her struggles &amp; admire her for trying in spite of that to help others &amp; clearly ma</span>
  <span id="freeText9204444228537183097" style="display:none">Honestly, more like two stars -- not in my opinion a very accurate representation of core Buddhist teachings, the amount of focus on the autobiographical seemed very heavy. More than anything, it felt quite redundant &amp; "padded" -- would have made a decent blog post of a couple pages, but really for me not even enough meaningful content to merit a full article, let alone a book. But that said, I definitely feel for her struggles &amp; admire her for trying in spite of that to help others &amp; clearly many other readers have found it (far) more helpful than I did, so I am glad it's out there &amp; hope you may find it more edifying than I....</span>
